      "text": "| Request Type | Routes To                    |\n|--------------|------------------------------|\n| default      | gemini, gemini-2.5-pro       |\n| background   | gemini, gemini-2.0-flash     |\n| think        | gemini, gemini-2.5-pro       |\n| longContext  | gemini, gemini-2.5-pro       |\n| webSearch    | gemini, gemini-2.5-flash     |",
